<p>Hi all,<p></p>Just for the record, I have replied to Robert offline. I don't think anyone was (badly) offended here. Just a few "gahads" got rankled... Welcome to the passionate side of Earthdawn! *grin*<p></p>Anyway, I still want to stress that we are interested in constructive debate, positive or concerned. And we look forward to some detailed contributions from you in the future Robert!<p></p>Now, back to the grindstone. *smile*<p></p>Take care,<p></p>JAMES FLOWERS<br>Line Developer, RedBrick Limited</p>
